<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6564567>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. a. Pronotal plate of Acanthaegilopsis sp. in anterior view. b. Xyalaspis sp., mesoscutum in lateral view. c. Aegilips sp., mesoscutum in lateral view. d. Aegilips zaitzevi Kovalev, 1974, head in anterior view. e. Aegilips nitidulus Dalman, 1823, forewing venation. f. Aegilips romseyensis Fergusson, 1985, head in anterior view. g. Aegilips zaitzevi Kovalev, 1974, forewing venation." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6564567/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6564571>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. a. Aegilips insularis Mata-Casanova & Pujade-Villar sp. nov, 2014, ♂, mesosoma in dorsal view. b. A. insularis, ♀, mesosoma in dorsal view. c. A. romseyensis Fergusson, 1985, mesosoma in lateral view. d. A. nitidulus Dalman, 1823, mesosoma in lateral view. e. A. kozlovi Kovalev, 1974. f. A. romseyensis. g. A. nitidulus. h. A. zaitzevi Kovalev, 1974." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6564571/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6564573>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. a. Aegilips ustulatus Belizin, 1973, mesosoma in lateral view. b. A. longicellus Belizin, 1951, mesosoma in dorsal-lateral view. c. A. flavidicornis (Kieffer, 1911), mesosoma in dorsal view. d. A. atricornis Fergusson, 1985, mesosoma in dorsal view. e. A. atricornis, mesoscutum in lateral view. f. A. paucus Belizin, 1961, mesosoma in dorsal view. g. A. paucus, mesoscutum in lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6564573/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

